Usage: unassignTSV [-help]
                   {-netName <string> | -all | -signal | -power | -ground | -selected}

-help                 # Prints out the command usage
-all                  # Unassign all TSVs (bool, required)
-ground               # Unassign Ground TSVs (bool, required)
-netName <string>     # Unassign TSVs for this net (string, required)
-power                # Unassign Power TSVs (bool, required)
-selected             # Unassign selected TSVs (bool, required)
-signal               # Unassign Signal TSVs (bool, required)